summary: An email from an FBI agent in New York forwarding a message about a source who left voicemails and has information on Jeffrey Epstein, specifically mentioning Dublin. The email indicates the source sent a photo and is attempting to provide information to law enforcement.

events.title: Email about Epstein/Dublin information
events.description: An FBI agent forwards a message stating a source left two voicemails, sent a photo, and has information on Jeffrey Epstein related to Dublin.

keyFacts: A source contacted the FBI in February 2021 claiming to have information on Jeffrey Epstein.
The information is specifically related to Dublin.
The source left two voicemails and sent a photo to the FBI.
The communication was forwarded between FBI email addresses.
The document shows post-Epstein death investigative activity in 2021.
